import React from 'react'
import  { Box , Grid, Button } from '@mui/material'

    return (

            <Grid item xs={6} >
                <Box p={1}>
                    <ColorSelect label='Font' select='Red'/>

                </Box>
            </Grid>
            <Grid item xs={4} >
                <Box p={1}>
                </Box>
            </Grid>
            <Grid item xs={4} >
                <Box  p={1}>

            </Grid>
            <Grid item xs={4} >

            </Grid>

}
